\c 61
\s Dhavhidhi anovimba naMwari pakutambudzika kwake
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba; nomutengeranwa. Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 kuchema kwangu, Mwari, Teererai munyengetero wangu.
\v 2 Ndichadana kwamuri ndiri pamugumo wapasi,
\s kana mwoyo wangu waziya; Ndiperekedzerei kudombo randisingasvikiri.
\p
\v 3 Nokuti imi makanga muri utiziro hwangu,
\s Neshongwe yangu yakasimba kwandingatiza muvengi wangu.
\p
\v 4 Ndichagara patende renyu nokusingaperi;
\s Ndichavanda munyasi mamapapiro enyu.
\p
\v 5 Nokuti imi Mwari makanzwa mhiko dzangu;
\s Makadzosa nhaka yavanotya zita renyu.
\p
\v 6 Muchawedzera mazuva ohupenyu hwamambo;
\s Makore ake achaenzana
\s naamarudzi mazhinji.
\p
\v 7 Achagara pamberi paMwari nokusingaperi;
\s Mumugadzirire unyoro nezvokwadi, kuti zvimuchengete.
\p
\v 8 Naizvozvo ndichaimbira zita renyu nziyo dzokurumbidza nokusingaperi, Kuti ndiite mhiko dzangu zuva
\s rimwe nerimwe.
